                                        </td>
                                        <td class="bd-en" lang="en" dir="ltr">
                                            <p>Al Hadhri &amp; Partners Law Firm, duly organized under the laws of the State of Qatar under Commercial Register No. 212506, located at Al Baraha Tower, Lusail, 5th Floor, Doha, Qatar.</p>
                                            <p>Hereinafter referred to as the "First Party".</p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="bd-ar" lang="ar" dir="rtl">
                                            <p>السيد / <strong><t t-esc="candidate_name or '-'"/></strong></p>
                                            <p>تاريخ الميلاد: <t t-esc="birth_date or '-'"/>، الجنسية: <t t-esc="doc.bd_nationality or '-'"/></p>
